{"title":"几首枪杆诗","authors":["孙志深　刘玉容　曹树理"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":7,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"几首枪杆诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者按：下面几首诗是中国人民志愿军同志自己的创作，为战士们普遍喜爱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、火箭炮          孙志深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火箭炮，呱呱叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的来源美国造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运输队长蒋介石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给咱送来不要收条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这回抗美来援朝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国兵要挨美国炮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、手榴弹          刘玉容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手榴弹，真是强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗美援朝保国防，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了美军一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算了狗日的伙食账。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、钢盔  孙志深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小钢盔，二斤沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军戴上杀敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀一端把话喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俘虏美军一大群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四、扁担  曹树理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小扁担，七尺长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑起油桶上前方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们吃得身体壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多杀美军多缴枪。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}